attributes.Long form description: The student begins by aligning their legs. Next, they unscrew the middle bolt from the legs of the object. Once the bolt is removed, they align the seat with the legs to assemble them. The student then screws the first leg into place. After that, they insert screws and saddle washers into the other legs. Finally, they screw the remaining legs.
